title: Adventures in Iceland
itunes:title: Adventures in Iceland
itunes:subtitle: With the aid of his recently discovered diaries, Katherine Findlay tells the unusual story of Pike Ward – a Devon fish merchant who became an Icelandic knight in the early 20th century.
